<div id="about-the-community" class="section-spacer">
    <h2 class="sect-title">About Marlborough</h2>
    <div class="col-grid-2">
        <div>
            <p class="par-lg">A tranquil residential neighborhood in the north east quadrant of Calgary. Marlborough is one of the older communities in the city and is bound by the 36 Street E on the west, the Memorial Drive on the south, the 52 Street E on the east and the Trans-Canada Highway on the north.</p>
            <p class="par-xl">Established in the late sixties, the community in Marlborough is renowned for its old-world charm and is quite popular among contemporary homebuyers and investors alike. </p>
        </div>
